		<h1>Wesnoth Add-ons Server</h1>

		<p>The Wesnoth game client can connect to and download add-ons from the add-ons server using the <b>Add-ons</b> option from the main menu.</p>

		<p>Additionally, for reference purposes, archival of retired instances of the add-ons server for older game versions, and people who cannot use the game client for technical reasons or otherwise, we have made this web directory of current and past add-ons server instances available. You may have a look at the list of add-ons available from each one and optionally download their contents from here.</p>

		<h2>Current instances</h2>

		<ul>
			<li><a href="1.14/"><b>Stable 1.14</b></a> <span>(1.13.12&ndash;1.14.x)</span></li>
			<li><a href="1.16/"><b>Development 1.16</b></a> <span>(1.15.14&ndash;1.16.x)</span></li>
			<li><a href="1.15/"><b>Development 1.15</b></a> <span>(1.15.0&ndash;1.15.13)</span></li>
			<li><a href="1.12/">Old stable 1.12</a> <span>(1.11.10&ndash;1.12.x)</span></li>
			<li><a href="trunk/">Testing instance</a> <span>(no versions)</span></li>
		</ul>

